    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>
            <catalog>oercommons.org</catalog>
            <entry>1770206341</entry>
          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">Tree of Life</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Baum des Lebens</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Arbre de la vie</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Árvore da vida</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Albero di vita</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Δέντρο της ζωής</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Árbol de la vida</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">offers photos, descriptions, and other information documenting the diversity of the world's organisms. Learn about animals, arthropoda, eukaryotes, flowering plants, fungi, and terrestrial vertebrates. Explore genetic relationships among organisms.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">bietet Fotos, Beschreibungen und andere 
Informationen, welche die Verschiedenartigkeit der organismen der Welt
dokumentieren an. Erlernen Sie über Tiere, arthropoda, 
Eukaryotes, blühende Pflanzen, Pilze und terrestrische Wirbeltiere. 
Erforschen Sie genetische Verhältnisse unter organismen.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">offre des photos, des descriptions, et toute autre 
information documentant la diversité des organizations du monde. 
Renseignez-vous sur des animaux, l'arthropoda, des eukaryotes, 
des usines fleurissantes, des mycètes, et des vertébrés terrestres.
Explorez les rapports génétiques parmi des organizations.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">oferece fotos, descrições, e a outra informação
que documenta a diversidade dos organismos do mundo. Aprenda 
sobre animais, arthropoda, eukaryotes, plantas flowering, fungos, e 
vertebrados terrestrial. Explore relacionamentos genetic entre 
organismos.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">offre le foto, le descrizioni ed altre informazioni
che documentano la diversità degli organismi del mondo. Impari 
circa gli animali, il arthropoda, gli eucarioti, le piante flowering, 
i funghi ed i vertebrati terrestri. Esplori i rapporti genetici 
fra gli organismi.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">προσφέρει τις φωτογραφίες, τις περιγραφές, και άλλες 
πληροφορίες τεκμηριώνοντας την ποικιλομορφία των παγκόσμιων 
οργανισμών. Μάθετε για τα ζώα, το arthropoda, 
eukaryotes, τα ανθίζοντας φυτά, τους μύκητες, και τα επίγεια 
σπονδυλωτά. Ερευνήστε τις γενετικές σχέσεις μεταξύ των 
οργανισμών.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">ofrece las fotos, las descripciones, y la otra 
información que documenta la diversidad de los organismos del mundo. 
Aprenda sobre animales, arthropoda, eukaryotes, plantas 
florecientes, hongos, y vertebrados terrestres. Explore los 
lazos genéticos entre organismos.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciências Sociais</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Scienze Sociali</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Ciencias Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
